ruby-cairo
------------------------------------------
Ruby bindings for the cairo graphics engine.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.6-1
  libcairo2-1.8.10-1
  ruby-1.8.7_p72-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-2.20.51-2
  cygport-0.10.1-1
  gcc4-core-4.5.1-1
  make-3.81-2
  pkg-config-0.23b-10

Canonical website:
  http://cairographics.org/

Canonical download:
  http://cairographics.org/releases/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ruby-cairo-1.8.5-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ruby-cairo-1.8.5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ruby-cairo-1.8.5-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ruby-cairo-1.8.5-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Port Notes:

